00:24:29,031 --> 00:24:32,034
<i>Mentari disebut 'Kakek'.</i>

275
00:24:33,118 --> 00:24:35,495
<i>Bulan, 'Ibu'.</i>

276
00:24:36,663 --> 00:24:39,249
<i>Api, 'Ayah'.</i>

277
00:24:40,542 --> 00:24:42,586
<i>Mereka menyebutnya 'Bulan Bunga'</i>

278
00:24:42,586 --> 00:24:47,633
<i>ketika bunga kecil tersebar
di bukit pohon ek dan padang rumput.</i>

279
00:24:48,175 --> 00:24:49,635
<i>Ada banyak.</i>

280
00:24:49,635 --> 00:24:55,432
<i>Begitu banyak,
