01:17:05,979 --> 01:17:07,356
Jangan sampai Maggie melihatnya.

914
01:17:07,356 --> 01:17:09,900
Dia punya mata, Henry.

915
01:17:09,900 --> 01:17:12,152
Terakhir kali dia memergokiku,
